    "name": {
      "zh": "Arsenal AK 7.62x39 四棘消焰器",
      "en": "AK 7.62x39 Arsenal 4 Piece Flash Hider"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "ARS 4P",
      "en": "ARS 4P"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "一款知名的膛口装置，在俄罗斯市场上常被称作“保加利亚型”枪口。其倒锥形结构能显著减小射击时的枪口火焰，在室内射击时还能起到减少枪口冲击波的效果。可兼容 5.45 至 7.62 毫米口径的各类 AK 平台，使用对应的膛口转接器还可加装至 AKM 或 AK-12 突击步枪上。",
      "en": "A well-known muzzle device commonly called \"The Bulgarian\" in Russia. Its reverse-cone shape makes it highly effective at reducing muzzle flash, and it also slightly lessens the concussive effect when firing indoors. Compatible with any caliber from 5.45 to 7.62 on the AK-74 platform, or with the appropriate adapter on AKM or AK-12 assault rifles."
    },
